---
import { FeaturedSVG } from '../config'
---

<div class='relative overflow-hidden bg-white dark:bg-gray-900'>
  <div class='mx-auto max-w-7xl'>
    <div
      class='relative z-10 bg-white pb-8 dark:bg-gray-900 sm:pb-16 md:pb-20 lg:w-full lg:max-w-2xl lg:pb-28 xl:pb-32'
    >
      <svg
        class='absolute inset-y-0 right-0 hidden h-full w-48 translate-x-1/2 transform text-white dark:text-gray-900 lg:block'
        fill='currentColor'
        viewBox='0 0 100 100'
        preserveAspectRatio='none'
        aria-hidden='true'
      >
        <polygon points='50,0 100,0 50,100 0,100'></polygon>
      </svg>
      <main
        class='mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 pt-10 sm:px-6 sm:pt-12 md:pt-16 lg:px-8 lg:pt-20 xl:pt-28'
      >
        <div class='text-center sm:text-left'>
          <h1
            class='text-left text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl'
          >
            <span class='block xl:inline'>Earn Money Online</span>{' '}
            <span class='block text-green-700 dark:text-green-300 xl:inline'>Digital Income Guide</span>
          </h1>
          <p
            class='mt-3 text-base text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 sm:mx-auto sm:mt-5 sm:max-w-xl sm:text-lg md:mt-5 md:text-xl lg:mx-0'
          >
            Howdy, your quest to earn money online starts here! In this guide, you'll discover 
            side hustles, online jobs, and business opportunities online and offline.
          </p>
          <p
            class='mt-3 text-base text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 sm:mx-auto sm:mt-5 sm:max-w-xl sm:text-lg md:mt-5 md:text-xl lg:mx-0'
          >
            It doesn't matter what your current situation is; college student, construction
            worker, accountant, convicted felon, or jobless. Nor, does it matter where you 
            live, anyone can generate income online! 
          </p>
          <p
            class='mt-3 text-base text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 sm:mx-auto sm:mt-5 sm:max-w-xl sm:text-lg md:mt-5 md:text-xl lg:mx-0'
          >
          Ready to boost your income? Discover proven ways to make money online and achieve 
          your financial goals. Start your journey to success with side hustles or explore 
          digital income ideasâ€”your path to earning online begins here!
          </p>
          <div class='mt-5 sm:mt-8 sm:flex sm:justify-center lg:justify-start'>
            <div class='rounded-md shadow'>
              <a
                href='/digtial-income-ideas'
                class='flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-transparent bg-green-100 px-8 py-3 text-base font-medium text-green-800 hover:bg-orange-200 dark:bg-green-700 dark:text-green-100 dark:hover:bg-orange-700 md:px-10 md:py-4 md:text-lg'
              >
                Start
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </main>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class='bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-500 lg:absolute lg:inset-y-0 lg:right-0 lg:w-1/2'>
    <img
      class='h-56 w-full object-cover sm:h-72 md:h-96 lg:h-full lg:w-full'
      src={FeaturedSVG.src}
      alt='featured'
    />
  </div>
</div>
